Class ViewResources

Represents a collection of resources used during the compilation of a view.

    Creates an instance of ViewResources.

    Parameters

    • Optional parent: ViewResources

      The parent resources. This resources can override them, but if a resource is not found, it will be looked up in the parent.

    • Optional viewUrl: string

      The url of the view to which these resources apply.
